discussing your anger issues.

01:55.783 --> 01:57.549
Anger issues?

01:57.551 --> 01:59.551
Anger issues?!

01:59.553 --> 02:00.986
Anger issues?

02:00.988 --> 02:03.155
Anger issues?!

02:03.157 --> 02:06.058
Yeah, all right, I'm afraid
our 50 minutes are almost up.

02:06.060 --> 02:08.127
Sorry. You were saying?

02:11.164 --> 02:13.565
(sighs) monty, I give up.

02:13.567 --> 02:15.968
After only 70 years of therapy?

02:15.970 --> 02:17.002
You're never gonna change.

02:17.004 --> 02:19.505
You-you will never have this.

02:19.507 --> 02:22.574
A cheap piece of plastic
with photos of ugly people?

02:22.576 --> 02:25.511
That is my family--
people who love me.

02:25.513 --> 02:26.845
Yes, you're right.

02:26.847 --> 02:28.914
I should consider
encasing people in plastic.

02:28.916 --> 02:31.483
Then I could always see
the look of fear in their faces.

02:31.485 --> 02:33.685
