14:44.017 --> 14:45.183
Just friends.

14:45.185 --> 14:46.584
Eh, we shall see.

14:46.586 --> 14:48.386
There is one test
for a-romance

14:48.388 --> 14:50.388
That never fails.

14:50.390 --> 14:52.423
Enjoy it.

14:57.696 --> 15:00.198
That is not a-love!

15:00.200 --> 15:02.400
This is the best--
we're friends,

15:02.402 --> 15:04.202
No one has any reason
to get upset,

15:04.204 --> 15:05.904
And no one gets hurt.

15:05.906 --> 15:07.372
To no one getting hurt.

15:07.374 --> 15:08.606
