15:13.013 --> 15:16.414
Excuse me,
do I ever get a joke?

15:16.416 --> 15:17.582
Keep rolling.

15:17.584 --> 15:20.518
"mr. Vice president,
madam speaker,

15:20.520 --> 15:22.287
"chinese overlords,

15:22.289 --> 15:25.623
Years ago, our forefathers,
and <i>foremothers..."</i>

15:25.625 --> 15:27.025
Burns:
Stick to the script!

15:27.027 --> 15:28.626
Oh, you try to
give direction

15:28.628 --> 15:29.794
To a bunch
of land apes

15:29.796 --> 15:32.297
Who aren't worth
the ping-pong balls

15:32.299 --> 15:34.699
Stuck to their
untalented asses!

15:34.701 --> 15:36.467
Idiots!
Mountebanks!

15:36.469 --> 15:38.369
Featherwits!
Poltroons!

15:38.371 --> 15:39.604
