17:00.820 --> 17:01.986
I took a tab.

17:01.988 --> 17:04.022
No, I'm not
gonna take the lessons,

17:04.024 --> 17:06.190
I just needed
to blow my nose.

17:06.192 --> 17:08.559
Ooh, my family's here.
Gotta go.

17:08.561 --> 17:10.361
Hey, guys!
It's good to see you.

17:10.363 --> 17:12.363
Hmm. Good to see you.

17:12.365 --> 17:13.831
Who were you talking to?

17:13.833 --> 17:14.866
My friend julia.

17:14.868 --> 17:17.168
<i>Julia?</i> Like a girl?

17:17.170 --> 17:18.569
She's not a girl.

17:18.571 --> 17:20.505
She's three years younger
than your mother.

17:20.507 --> 17:21.639
