17:24.811 --> 17:26.811
Our deepest thoughts
and feelings.

17:26.813 --> 17:27.879
Mm-hmm.

17:27.881 --> 17:31.082
Kids, could you
leave the room, please?

17:31.084 --> 17:33.918
Faster!

17:33.920 --> 17:34.986
Geronimo!

17:34.988 --> 17:35.887
(retreating footsteps)

17:35.889 --> 17:37.855
Marge, it's nothing.

17:37.857 --> 17:39.824
She's just
my new best friend.

17:39.826 --> 17:42.493
(groans angrily)

17:42.495 --> 17:43.728
What the-- why--

17:43.730 --> 17:45.329
Why are you mad
at those eggs?!

17:45.331 --> 17:47.265
They didn't do anything!

17:47.267 --> 17:48.766
Homer simpson!

17:48.768 --> 17:51.002
(whimpering)

17:51.004 --> 17:53.371
After all I've put up with
for all these years,

17:53.373 --> 17:55.773
If I'm not
your best friend,

17:55.775 --> 17:57.775
What is this marriage about?!

17:57.777 --> 17:59.544
Okay, okay, you're
my best friend.

17:59.546 --> 18:01.913
She's just somebody I call
when I'm mad at you.

18:02.881 --> 18:03.915
