18:33.613 --> 18:36.981
And, marge, <i>I</i> love you
as much as that bike.

18:36.983 --> 18:38.583
You <i>are</i> the bike.

18:38.585 --> 18:40.017
(gasps) wha...?!

18:42.321 --> 18:43.788
